'''Abdelmouhib Chamakh''' ({{langx|ar|مهيب الشامخ}}; born 25 August 2001) is a Tunisian professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]] for [[Tunisian Ligue Professionnelle 1]] club [[Club Africain]] and the [[Tunisia national football team|Tunisia national team]].

==Club career==
Chamakh began his senior career with [[CO Médenine]] in 2017, as they were relegated to the [[Tunisian Ligue Professionnelle 2]]. In 2022, he transferred to [[ES Métlaoui]] in the [[Tunisian Ligue Professionnelle 1]] and on 5 August 2023 extended his contract with them for 2 more season.And in 2026 he won his first trophy with club africain making it its first trophy he has ever won<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ar.lemaghreb.tn/%D8%B1%D9%8A%D8%A7%D8%B6%D8%A9/item/92491-%D9%85%D9%87%D9%8A%D8%A8-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B4%D8%A7%D9%85%D8%AE-%D9%8A%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%B5%D9%84-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AA%D8%AC%D8%B1%D8%A8%D8%A9-%D9%85%D8%B9-%D9%86%D8%AC%D9%85-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D8%AA%D9%84%D9%88%D9%8A|title=جريدة المغرب &#124; مهيب الشامخ يواصل التجربة مع نجم المتلوي|website=ar.lemaghreb.tn}}</ref> He played 53 matches in all competitions with ES Métlaoui.<ref name="auto">{{Cite web|url=https://al-ain.com/article/world-cup-tunisia-story|title=من ملاعب الظل إلى كأس العالم.. قصة استثنائية في منتخب تونس|first=العين|last=الإخبارية|date=15 May 2026|website=العين الإخبارية}}</ref> On 1 July 2025, he transferred to [[Club Africain]] on a contract until 2029.<ref name="auto1"/> He helped Club Africain win the [[2025–26 Tunisian Ligue Professionnelle 1]] as the starting goalkeeper.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.france24.com/ar/%D8%B1%D9%8A%D8%A7%D8%B6%D8%A9/20260511-%D9%86%D8%A7%D8%AF%D9%8A-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D9%81%D8%B1%D9%8A%D9%82%D9%8A-%D9%8A%D9%83%D8%B3%D8%B1-%D8%B5%D9%8A%D8%A7%D9%85-10-%D8%B3%D9%86%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D9%88%D9%8A%D8%AA%D9%88%D8%AC-%D8%A8%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AF%D9%88%D8%B1%D9%8A-%D8%B9%D9%84%D9%89-%D8%AD%D8%B3%D8%A7%D8%A8-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AA%D8%B1%D8%AC%D9%8A|title=تونس: النادي الأفريقي يكسر صيام 10 سنوات ويتوج بالدوري على حساب الترجي|date=11 May 2026|website=فرانس 24 / France 24}}</ref>

==International career==
Chamakh made his official debut with the senior team in a 0–0 friendly tie with [[Canada men's national soccer team|Canada]] on 31 March 2026.<ref name="auto"/> He made the final squad for the [[2026 FIFA World Cup]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/articles/cy42jjj4gg4o|title=Tunisia boss Sabri Lamouchi leaves Ferjani Sassi out of World Cup squad|date=15 May 2026|website=BBC Sport}}</ref>

